                <head>342. Editorial Note</head>
                <p>On February 6, 1963, Greece deposited its instrument of ratification of the 1953
                    Opium Protocol. The Protocol then entered into force on March 8. (Circular
                    airgram CA–8445, February 7; National Archives and Records Administration,
                        <gloss target="#t_RG1">RG</gloss> 59, Central Files 1960–63, SOC 11–5)</p>
            </div>
